  <h3>2. {membrane.name} — Best for Groups and Families</h3>
  <p>When you are camping with family or a group of friends, the Membrane Solutions straw is affordable enough that everyone can have their own dedicated filter. At {getPriceTier(membrane.price)} per straw, equipping a group of four costs very little — a small price for guaranteed water safety. The 0.1-micron hollow fiber membrane technology is the same proven filtration used in premium backpacking filters costing three times as much.</p>
