  <p>The critical advantage of tablets over filters is virus removal. Filter straws with 0.1-micron membranes physically cannot capture viruses, which are as small as 0.02 microns. In contaminated waters where viral threats exist, Aquatabs provide the protection that filters miss. At just {getPriceTier(aquatabs.price)} for 30 tablets and weighing under an ounce, there is no good reason to leave camp without them.</p>
